info.author: Leon Dong
info.description:
A Python Library for translation between traditional Chinese and simplified Chinese. Support Python2 and Python3. Thanks Thomas to provid Python3 support.
Jianfan是一个关于中文繁简转换的函数库。简体中文和繁体中文转换提供了两个函数:jtof(unistr)和ftoj(unistr).
